fields.value:
set terminal svg fname "Arial" fsize 10 size 960,420
set output '{graph_hash}.svg'
set datafile separator ","
set xtics out
set ytics out
set xtics nomirror
set ytics nomirror
set key bottom left outside horizontal

set nobox
set auto x
set key reverse Left spacing 1.35
set style line 80 lt 1 pt 0 lc rgb '#000000' lw 0.25
set grid linestyle 80
set grid noxtics

set macro
OUTPUT_EPS="set terminal postscript eps solid color 'Helvetica' 18 size 5, 2.5; set output '{graph_hash}.eps'"
OUTPUT_WIDEEPS="set terminal postscript eps solid color 'Helvetica' 18 size 10, 2.2; set output '{graph_hash}.wide.eps'"

COL(INDEX) = INDEX*3+4
VAL(INDEX) = column(COL(INDEX))
EL(INDEX) = COL(INDEX)+1
EH(INDEX) = COL(INDEX)+2
STR(INDEX) = stringcolumn(COL(INDEX))
VALFILTER(INDEX,FILTERINDEX,FILTERVAL)=(stringcolumn(FILTERINDEX) eq FILTERVAL ? VAL(INDEX) : 1/0)

set ylabel "{ylabel}"
set style data histogram
set bars .5
set style fill solid 1.0 border -1
set boxwidth 1
set xtic rotate by -30

{line_colors}

set style histogram errorbars gap 1 lw 0.25
plot for [I=0:{num_cols}-1] "{graph_hash}.csv" u (VAL(I)):EL(I):EH(I):xtic(3) ls I+1 title col(COL(I))

@OUTPUT_EPS
replot

@OUTPUT_WIDEEPS
replot

set ylabel "{ylabel}"
set style data histogram
set bars .5
set style fill solid 1.0 border -1
set boxwidth 1
set xtic rotate by -30

{line_colors}


set style histogram gap 1
plot for [I=0:{num_cols}-1] "{graph_hash}.csv" u (VAL(I)):xtic(3) ls I+1 title col(COL(I))

@OUTPUT_EPS
replot

@OUTPUT_WIDEEPS
replot

set ylabel "{ylabel}"
set style data linespoints
set bars .5
set style fill solid 1.0 border -1
set boxwidth 1

{line_colors}

plot for [I=0:{num_cols}-1] "{graph_hash}.csv" u (column(3)):(VALFILTER(I,1,"data")):xtic(3)  title col(COL(I)) w lines, for [I=0:{num_cols}-1] "" u (column(3)):(VALFILTER(I,1,"data")):EL(I):EH(I) lw 3 notitle w yerr

@OUTPUT_EPS
replot

@OUTPUT_WIDEEPS
replot

set ylabel "{ylabel}"
set style data linespoints
set bars .5
set style fill solid 1.0 border -1
set boxwidth 1

{line_colors}

plot for [I=0:{num_cols}-1] "{graph_hash}.csv" u (VALFILTER(I,1,"data")):xtic(3) lw 3 title col(COL(I)) w lines

@OUTPUT_EPS
replot

@OUTPUT_WIDEEPS
replot

set ylabel "cumulative"
set style data linespoints
set bars .5
set style fill solid 1.0 border -1
set boxwidth 1

{line_colors}

CVAL(T,I)=(I == {num_cols} ? T : CVAL(T+VAL(I),I+1))
CVALFILTER(INDEX,FILTERINDEX,FILTERVAL)=(stringcolumn(FILTERINDEX) eq FILTERVAL ? CVAL(0,I) : 1/0)

plot for [I=0:{num_cols}-1] "{graph_hash}.csv" u (CVALFILTER(I,1,"data")):xtic(3) lt I+1 title col(COL(I)) w filledcurves x1

@OUTPUT_EPS
replot

@OUTPUT_WIDEEPS
